{"id": 2374, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x美诺】在清理家里的灰尘垃圾方面，你对什么心存恐惧？", "description": "不是我受不了，是估计大家都会受不了", "record_count": 8598, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180525121631H8WMzsOPCtaxbj3L.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 285185, "content": "头发和小强和老鼠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268640}, {"id": 288006, "content": "把东西都塞到柜子里\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169201}, {"id": 283913, "content": "猫毛 猫毛 猫毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334072}, {"id": 283914, "content": "讨厌灰尘，本身有鼻炎，一吸就想打喷嚏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356315}, {"id": 283915, "content": "我自己的头发??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356385}, {"id": 283916, "content": "有一堆小动物在安居", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356433}, {"id": 283923, "content": "虫子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351084}, {"id": 285204, "content": "qq", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1306658}, {"id": 283925, "content": "吸尘后空气可能更加灰了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548184}, {"id": 285205, "content": "wq", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1306658}, {"id": 285206, "content": "jjhh", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1306658}, {"id": 283930, "content": "丢东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164980}, {"id": 283931, "content": "\n新搬的家，很脏……崩溃…花大价钱去购置小家电…清理…不如叫个保洁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356499}, {"id": 285211, "content": "软体动物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362233}, {"id": 283932, "content": "头发缠绕湿了的灰尘 老鼠屎 被老鼠咬烂的塑料袋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562057}, {"id": 283936, "content": "狗…狗毛?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341462}, {"id": 284448, "content": "灰尘满天飞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359371}, {"id": 288288, "content": "测试测试测试测测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试", "image": "img/option/option/20180620135647j3AYTeIOa6fytlhg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314813}, {"id": 284195, "content": "想扔又不舍得扔的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358500}, {"id": 283686, "content": "植物掉的叶子、猫砂什么的吸尘器吸不干净，还是要手捡", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283687, "content": "吸地板倒还好，清理收集灰尘的盒子真是崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 299, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283688, "content": "吸尘器超大声，猫猫狗狗害怕，有人休息也不能用", "image": null, "praise_count": 171, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283689, "content": "总有沟沟缝缝清理不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 575, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283691, "content": "空气很脏，每天浮尘就够受的，不开窗又闷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 284208, "content": "头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320867}, {"id": 285233, "content": "徒手活捉老鼠?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348297}, {"id": 283954, "content": "水池霉渍 滑滑的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189267}, {"id": 283965, "content": "灰尘过敏性鼻炎，喷嚏没完", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116914}, {"id": 283718, "content": "角落有猫蹭的屎在生蛆", "image": null, "praise_count": 164, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057898}, {"id": 283719, "content": "突然翻出的一窝小强……这时死的心都有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1761, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354772}, {"id": 283720, "content": "清理卫生间地漏了解一下?", "image": null, "praise_count": 714, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354782}, {"id": 283721, "content": "镂空的家具，真心不想拿抹布一点点抠着擦，所以家具能怎么简约就怎么简约，去T*M*D好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 942, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624387}, {"id": 283722, "content": "传统的木桌，桌面上每边都有一道不大不小的缝，每次清理起来都很崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624387}, {"id": 283724, "content": "蜘蛛", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333885}, {"id": 283725, "content": "当然是飘起来的灰尘啊，鼻子会十分难受啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 369, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354795}, {"id": 283726, "content": "擦灰太烦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028583}, {"id": 283727, "content": "头发！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1068, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179273}, {"id": 283728, "content": "一眼望去全是灰，没有一块净土（顿时不想动好吗！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351961}, {"id": 283729, "content": "翻开某个角落，忽然跑出只蜘蛛，小强，蛾子啥的，真的是扔了东西就跑", "image": null, "praise_count": 449, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319544}, {"id": 283730, "content": "灰和头发最受不了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354828}, {"id": 283731, "content": "纱窗外侧那面，太?容易清洁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354837}, {"id": 283732, "content": "犄角旮旯里的灰尘什么的，最头疼了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020655}, {"id": 283733, "content": "头发，还有一窝虫卵，想起来都要起鸡皮疙瘩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349595}, {"id": 283734, "content": "各位，显微镜下的螨虫了解下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 188, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305739}, {"id": 283735, "content": "木地板 \n木地板 \n木地板 \n多年后.....\n裂缝的木地板 \n裂缝的木地板 \n裂缝的木地板", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354852}, {"id": 283736, "content": "永远收拾不完孩子的玩具。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325816}, {"id": 283739, "content": "发现有白蚁窝……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084163}, {"id": 283740, "content": "要是小区内有送菜服务怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354932}, {"id": 283741, "content": "马云脑子是什么构造的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354932}, {"id": 283742, "content": "头发头发头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352545}]}